concise "Risk Debate" as RD
concise "Portfolio Manager" as PM
concise "Memory / IO" as MEM

@0
MA is Idle
NA is Idle
SA is Idle
FA is Idle
ID is Idle
TR is Idle
RD is Idle
PM is Idle
MEM is {Resolving Pending}

@5
MEM is Idle
MA is {Fetching\nData}

@20
MA is {LLM\nAnalysis}

@35
MA is Idle
