note top of MA
  Each analyst loops:
  tool_call → result → tool_call → ...
  until LLM stops calling tools
end note

note top of ID
  N=2 debate rounds shown.
  Configurable via
  max_debate_rounds.
end note

note top of RD
  M=2 risk rounds shown.
  Configurable via
  max_risk_discuss_rounds.
end note

@enduml
